title: Putting The Income in Fixed Income | Bright Ideas
description:
Sponsored by Fidelity

Does the word “income” get your attention? With fixed-income investing, tools like bonds have the potential to generate more return than keeping money in a savings account. In this episode of “Bright Ideas,” Fidelity’s Adam Kramer joins host Rod Thill to share strategies that put the “income” in fixed-income investing, and how this can apply to the goals on your horizon.

Catch up on Season 2 of “Bright Ideas” at https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmur3Z0Afau6TsU9HhmWfe4JNeMHA4R1r

And you can learn more about types of fixed-income investing tools here: https://www.fidelity.com/brightideas
